{'id': 35015055, 'body': "Hi there. For P2P related orders, you can refer to our P2P transaction policy here: https://www.binance.com/en/support/faq/p2p-user-transaction-policy-360041066751

Alternatively, you can submit an appeal if it's still on time. Kindly refer to our P2P appeal handling rules: https://www.binance.com/en/support/faq/binance-p2p-appeal-handling-rules-360041839052

If you need further assistance, kindly connect with our live chat at:  http://binance.com/en/chat  Thankyou -AT", 'modified': '2023-02-22T13:24:53Z'}

{'id': 36190482, 'body': 'Hello, we are here to help! 

For us to check properly and advise you. kindly edit your review and inform us of the Case ID. 

You can also create another chat at Binance.com/en/chat - FP', 'modified': '2023-04-26T20:17:53Z'}

{'id': 38474169, 'body': 'Hello Abdullah!

Thanks for contacting us and checking on this. We can confirm that Binance does not have a partnership or cooperation with this project.Blockchain platforms, such as BNB Chain, provide the opportunity for anyone to launch their own projects and coins.This means that various projects can be created and exist independently without any direct involvement or endorsement from Binance. ^BT



', 'modified': '2023-08-23T08:58:37Z'}

{'id': 33748498, 'body': "Hi there, thank you for letting us know. Your review is appreciated. Could you clear your app cache and try again? Open your APP and select Profile > Settings > Clear Cache.
If the issue persists, kindly access it via your browser and submit your appeal via: https://p2p.binance.com/en/trade. If you need further assistance, don't hesitate to contact us at: Binance.com/en/chat. -RA.

", 'modified': '2022-12-15T18:08:30Z'}

{'id': 31823834, 'body': 'Hi, please allow us to make things right for you. You may try to log in further with the following tips.

1, Clean up the APP caches and cookies, then terminate the background process;
2, Delete the APP data.
3, Switch Wifi to mobile data service.
If problem persists, enter your home>personal profile page>help&support>chat to submit.

Alternatively, you may log in to your account via the web(PC) and click the "chatbox" to start a live chat.', 'modified': '2022-09-05T01:05:44Z'}

{'id': 38454703, 'body': "Hello Ahmad!
Thanks for contacting us and checking on this. We can confirm that Binance does not have a partnership or cooperation with this project. This project is also not listed in our exchange platform. We strongly urge all of our users to exercise caution and conduct thorough research and due diligence before investing in any project. While we strive to provide a secure and reliable platform, it's also essential for users to take the initiative to research and assess the legitimacy of any project they consider investing in. Do be reminded to always do your own research. If you have any further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact us at binance.com/en/chat. Stay SAFU! ^BT


", 'modified': '2023-08-22T12:00:14Z'}

{'id': 22870902, 'body': "We apologize for the problems you’re facing. We'd love to try and resolve your issue ASAP.

Please edit your review with your chat ID so a member of our support team will look into your case at the earliest. Thanks!
", 'modified': '2021-05-18T09:27:38Z'}

{'id': 34670345, 'body': 'Dear, noted on your feedback. May we confirm if the issue's resolved? If not, please try to log in further with the following instructions.

1. Update your APP to the latest version;
2. Clean up the APP caches and cookies, then terminate the background process;
3. Delete the APP data.
4. Switch Wifi to mobile data service.
If still not work, enter your home>personal profile page>help&support>chat to submit.

Alternatively, you may log in to your account via the web(PC) and click the ""chatbox"" to start a live chat. - SM', 'modified': '2023-02-04T07:56:02Z'}

