{'id': 35096867, 'body': "Hi there, you can choose to withdraw via other networks. Please refer to the fees table here:https://www.binance.com/en/fee/cryptoFee. Insert BTC at the search option and you will be able to see the withdrawal fees of various networks. 

You can choose your desired network to make the withdrawals. However, please remember to check your receiver's address that allows matching the same network that you have chosen to withdraw. Otherwise, you may lose your crypto if the selected network is not supported by the platform/wallet. 

If you need further assistance, kindly contact our live chat support at: https://www.binance.com/en/chat. Thanks! ", 'modified': '2023-02-27T13:16:47Z'}

